# common git commands

## new branch
```sh
git checkout -b new-branch

or

git branch new-branch
git checkout new-branch
```

## update and commit
```sh
git add .
git commit -m "git test"

git push -u origin new-branch
```


# Startup

## Preparations
Docker Desktop
Go

## MySQL/Redis in Docker
打开Docker Desktop 并登录
### MySQL
In cmd
```cmd
docker run -d --name seuoj-mysql --restart unless-stopped ^
  -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD=seuseuseu ^
  -e MYSQL_DATABASE=ojdb ^
  -p 3307:3306 ^
  mysql:8
```
// params: --name docker容器名; PASSWORD为mysql密码; DATABASE为数据库名; -p 3307:3306 为端口映射; mysql:8 为镜像名;

等待约 10-30 秒，直到 MySQL 就绪。可查看日志：
```cmd
docker logs seuoj-mysql
```

### Redis
In cmd
```cmd
docker run -d --name seuoj-redis --restart unless-stopped ^
  -p 6379:6379 ^
  redis:7
```

## 初始化表结构
In cmd
```cmd
docker exec -i seuoj-mysql mysql -uroot -pseuseuseu ojdb < "e:\codes\advanced-ds\seuoj\seu-oj-backend\database\user.sql"
docker exec -i seuoj-mysql mysql -uroot -pseuseuseu ojdb < "e:\codes\advanced-ds\seuoj\seu-oj-backend\database\problems.sql"
docker exec -i seuoj-mysql mysql -uroot -pseuseuseu ojdb < "e:\codes\advanced-ds\seuoj\seu-oj-backend\database\problem_testcases.sql"
docker exec -i seuoj-mysql mysql -uroot -pseuseuseu ojdb < "e:\codes\advanced-ds\seuoj\seu-oj-backend\database\submissions.sql"
docker exec -i seuoj-mysql mysql -uroot -pseuseuseu ojdb < "e:\codes\advanced-ds\seuoj\seu-oj-backend\database\submission_results.sql"
```

## seu-oj-backend/config/config.yaml
修改部分地方
```yaml
server:
  host: "0.0.0.0"
  port: "8080"

database:
  host: "127.0.0.1"
  port: "3307"
  user: "root"
  password: "seuseuseu"
  name: "ojdb"

redis:
  addr: "127.0.0.1:6379"
  password: ""
  db: 0

auth:
  jwt_secret: "seu-oj-dev-secret"

sandbox:
  docker_image: "gcc:13"
  compile_image: ""
  run_image: ""
  user: "65534:65534"
  cpus: "1.0"
  memory_mb: 256
  pids_limit: 64
  tmpfs_mb: 64
  file_size_kb: 1024
  output_limit_kb: 256
  compile_output_kb: 256
  read_only_rootfs: true
  compile_timeout_sec: 15
  run_timeout_buffer_ms: 500
```

## 拉判题镜像
```sh
docker pull gcc:13
```

## 启动后端（两个进程）
```sh
cd ./seu-oj-backend # 假设当前目录为项目seuoj根目录
go mod download
```

### 终端1
```sh
go run .
```

### 终端2
```sh
go run ./cmd/judge-worker
```

## 启动
浏览器访问[http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)

自检接口：[http://localhost:8080/api/health](http://localhost:8080/api/health)

docker检查: `docker ps`